LINES.text:
We hadn’t even considered finding
materials during the very first visit.

Come on, leave it, two pieces
of the fence, that’s enough...

No one’s doing something
for the other person,

He’s been living with the
shrapnel for three years now

When the first Alazan rocket was
fired from the neighbouring village,

And what's phenomenal
is that no one wants wars
But one thing is for sure:

Only two of them
survived out of five.
